{"id": "1428816742699765900", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "author_id": "497560030078566420", "author_name": "beeswithtea", "content": "heyhey!! I’m lookin’ to build a team around Jenkin >:3\n\nI’ve been running Jenkin/Ramona/Ogier/Tawil, and it works pretty well, but I kinda feel like I’m short for mana (and Tawil and Jenkin fight for who gets to put a card into Ultra Space each turn).\n\n~~also, I did build Clementine! I thought she was a fun character in writing, and admittedly Flare’s fervent hatred of her amused me. I have no idea what she does.~~", "timestamp": "2025-10-17T18:47:37.591000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1428816742204838068", "filename": "IMG_1635.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 205171, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400749543288475770/1428816742204838068/IMG_1635.png?ex=6a358ec9&is=6a343d49&hm=ad3948e6d518d3fa7382b135c96e0ac091b92a962b077e113db067a4b79c237f&"}, {"id": "1428816742473535518", "filename": "IMG_1634.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 271684, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400749543288475770/1428816742473535518/IMG_1634.png?ex=6a358ec9&is=6a343d49&hm=a7fd67437785f5b7c4446afc32e6cb93246ffb94bec6943b7644c23ae77e653a&"}]}
{"id": "1428818504114507807", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "author_id": "706262934485073951", "author_name": "bagels5899", "content": "So now you have both Jenkins and Clem, both of them have strong synergy, if you wanna continue building around Jenkins then Castor is set to rerun soon and he’s just a really good Ultra support…\n\nfor now probably run Jenkins/Tawil/Clementine/Ogier and swap Ogier for Castor when (and if) you get him\n\nwhat Clementine does is give a ton of keyflare regen (so lots of posses), temp strength down, exalt can either be an emergency button or a burst turn tool and if she gets priority on ultra space the best strength stacker in the game\n\nidk how support Tawil works exactly but prioritize giving swarm impact into ultra space for bursting and other turns either Clem or Tawil\n\n-# not super experienced take this with a grain of salt", "timestamp": "2025-10-17T18:54:37.545000+00:00", "type": 19, "reply_to": "1428816742699765900"}
